{"tid":603611,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單版白切雞脾","createTime":"2018-03-24T01:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-24T14:51:22.000Z","uid":40542,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9327b3de1b8a7ba23c17031ccddb96f57d5c90f3","tid":603611,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094629_7b6fbd4c592d356e087a0f1053751007.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094629_7b6fbd4c592d356e087a0f1053751007.png&h=8ea64bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n材料有去骨雞脾，紅蔥頭，蔥，薑，鹽，生粉<br />\n可以用連骨嘅雞脾，但我屋企把刀太廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094538_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094538_4a47a0db6e60853dedfcfdf08a5ca249.png&h=87c98b52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浸隻雞兩三秒再拎返上來，如是者做3-4次<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094545_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094545_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png&h=2954928a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沖/浸冰水<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094548_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094548_09dd8c2662b96ce14928333f055c5580.png&h=68c3f340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抹乾後搵少少鹽醃，少少好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094551_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094551_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png&h=59c2932d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再上少少生粉，會令隻雞滑啲，少少好啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094555_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094555_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=a91b802c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n切啲薑片同蔥段，放落隻碟度同啲雞一齊蒸20分鍾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094602_602e8f042f463dc47ebfdf6a94ed5a6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094602_602e8f042f463dc47ebfdf6a94ed5a6d.png&h=94621f1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蒸緊嘅同時可以準備個薑蔥，切碎啲蔥同紅蔥頭，磨啲薑蓉，加啲鹽，再撈勻佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094606_7afbb1602613ec52b265d7a54ad27330.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094606_7afbb1602613ec52b265d7a54ad27330.png&h=75fedf96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094609_586e508f161f26ce94633729ac56c602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094609_586e508f161f26ce94633729ac56c602.png&h=e1384a82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夠鍾就熄火開蓋，篤隻塊子入去睇下熟味，流出來啲水係清的話就係熟<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094613_59b2900aa03cb2182a51cdb520b535b6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094613_59b2900aa03cb2182a51cdb520b535b6.png&h=6dd3c271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後贊啲滾油落去，再撈勻佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094622_c00b57557743e709b8b96933432e0dfa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094622_c00b57557743e709b8b96933432e0dfa.png&h=06afde55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搞掂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/24/094629_7b6fbd4c592d356e087a0f1053751007.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F24%2F094629_7b6fbd4c592d356e087a0f1053751007.png&h=8ea64bbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b6eb8f4f91613bf0b994b4f95b4255e2a33f2a4e","tid":603611,"uid":33059,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T01:58:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96808a85ef1870b7776cf84e2c4129362afa153","tid":603611,"uid":172376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:01:56.000Z","msg":"想睇點整口水雞多啲<br />\n個汁好難整得好食"},{"pid":"31ae4937433880836e98db1ddc7bffe82c1b0130","tid":603611,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b96808a85ef1870b7776cf84e2c4129362afa153","tid":603611,"uid":172376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:01:56.000Z","msg":"想睇點整口水雞多啲<br />\n個汁好難整得好食"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"收到，呢個weekend 整先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457c600684551cb29f40a320c95ccda9a7cb52f9","tid":603611,"uid":21423,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"890845963fef630e5f7542c42526c53af2c9a6cc","tid":603611,"uid":164167,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"457c600684551cb29f40a320c95ccda9a7cb52f9","tid":603611,"uid":21423,"like":20,"dislike":5,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:14:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T02:16:15.000Z","msg":"警方列作傻人發現案"},{"pid":"be853c1edd7ef872ad903135dda29a39233b0f8a","tid":603611,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited